{"tid":2432860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局拒認漏報病人打科興疫苗亡　全靠死者友人搵傳媒追查還原真相","createTime":"2021-03-04T15:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:58:05.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58c129f0c9a959d3f497186ce70b7500ee2bf284","tid":2432860,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/5L5CNYAHM5GD7OG6QKSBNB6UBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F5L5CNYAHM5GD7OG6QKSBNB6UBE%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=b1c1df43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F5L5CNYAHM5GD7OG6QKSBNB6UBE%2F&h=dc7b6fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/5L5CNYAHM5GD7OG6QKSBNB6UBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然63歲男子接種中國科興疫苗後死亡的報道已經刊登，但背後辛勞的追查，卻只換來醫管局連番為3日來沒通報的過錯辯護，矢口否認接獲傳媒查詢後，才認真調查事件的事實。真相仍未還原，相信死者親友心結難以放下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GKKDD37USFHNHJ5QBRGHIL3SV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGKKDD37USFHNHJ5QBRGHIL3SV4.png&h=57da9098&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8bc10d8d74a49c9e9d02f1a0fb62e1e84c4ea0d","tid":2432860,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />草菅人命 毫無人性"},{"pid":"3d2e6dd149686e72e411fa3c56d360e00c9dd0f5","tid":2432860,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8bc10d8d74a49c9e9d02f1a0fb62e1e84c4ea0d","tid":2432860,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />草菅人命 毫無人性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"喺醫院度做嘅人，本身對生生死死已麻木晒（唔識嘅人）"